In the drawings:
FIG. 1 is a configuration view of an apparatus for diagnosing a DC link capacitor according to the related art;
FIG. 2 is a configuration view of one exemplary embodiment illustrating an inverter system to which the present disclosure is applied and an apparatus for diagnosing a DC link capacitor according to the present disclosure;
FIGS. 3A to 3D are exemplary views showing a state of the inverter in response to the control of a controller of the diagnosis apparatus;
FIG. 4 is an exemplary view showing a switching waveform and a current state under control of the controller; and
FIG. 5 is an exemplary view showing the change in a discharge time responsive to voltage reduction, in a DC link capacitor in a normal state and in a deteriorated state.
